    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><span id="more"></span><h2 id="《雪后即景》"><a href="#《雪后即景》" class="headerlink" title="《雪后即景》"></a>《雪后即景》</h2><p>​                      现代(与deepseek共创)</p><p>​    推门惊见雪满檐，<br>​    手抖拍照冻成狗。<br>​    美景虽好心已凉，<br>​    回屋喝汤暖心头。</p><p><img src="/2025/02/07/%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%AA%E6%99%AF-%E6%B3%A8%E5%BE%90%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88%E6%8B%8D%E6%91%84-%EF%BC%88%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0test%EF%BC%89/myblog\source_posts\新年雪景-注徐大师拍摄-（照片上传test）.assets\image-20250207141548153.png" alt="image-20250207141548153"></p>]]></content>
    
    
